    <item>
      <title>印度推迟决定采取措施遏制期权狂热</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/india-defers-decision-on-steps-to-curb-frenzy-in-options-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度证券市场监管机构并未宣布限制衍生品交易激增的措施，尽管其对该国蓬勃发展的共同基金行业的规则进行了调整，但这一举动令投资者感到意外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/india-defers-decision-on-steps-to-curb-frenzy-in-options-trading</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 16:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国航空计划出售 13 亿美元股份以摆脱债务重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/thai-air-plans-1-3-billion-share-sale-to-complete-debt-revamp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国国际航空计划在 12 月前向债权人和其他投资者发行价值至少 420 亿泰铢（13 亿美元）的新股，这是退出法院监督的债务重组和恢复股票交易的重要一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/thai-air-plans-1-3-billion-share-sale-to-complete-debt-revamp</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 10:44:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
